snippet: The deal will give the British supermarket chain Tesco 20 percent of a new joint venture with China Resources Enterprise, which will have more than 3,000 outlets in China and Hong Kong.
abstract: The deal will give the British supermarket chain Tesco 20 percent of a new joint venture with China Resources Enterprise, which will have more than 3,000 outlets in China and Hong Kong.

headline.main: Tesco Plans Venture With Leading Chinese Grocery Chain
